# Claude Harness Kit — repository .gitignore (public)
#
# This kit repo contains only documentation, rules, skills, agents, hooks,
# and CI/PR templates — so this file mostly keeps OS/editor junk and
# local-only state out of the published history. Note: `.claude/` IS part
# of the kit and stays tracked — the only exceptions are the machine-local
# entries below (settings.local.json, cache/).

# ── OS junk ──────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
._*
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ── Editors / IDEs ───────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── Stray tool artifacts ─────────────────────────────────
.Rhistory
*.log

# ── Claude Code local state (machine-local, never publish) ──
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/cache/
CLAUDE.local.md

# ── Build/dependency dirs (if examples or tooling are ever added) ──
node_modules/
target/
dist/

# ── Packaging artifacts ──────────────────────────────────
*.zip
